            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-1">
            <img src="~/Images/冯浩正面照.jpg" class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" alt="Responsive image" />
            <p><strong>冯浩（Nick Feng）</strong> -- 美国佛吉尼亚州山南道大学伯德商学院MBA。</p>
